data.description: Come and see this beautiful yard and setting, it feels like a gem in the forest!  Located on a large corner lot, well cared for, one level home.  Partially updated, 3 bed, 2 bath with dedicated office space, built in desk.  Large kitchen, granite counter tops, newer laminate flooring plus large solid gorgeous marble tiles in the living room. New roof (2019) New furnace, new water heater.  Perfect setting among the pines, mature trees and landscaping.  Large back deck for entertaining, BBQs, parties.  The prefect Bend location!  Close to shopping and exploring, quiet setting yet near town and trails. Come see!
